[EventDate "2020.??.??"]

{[#] What is the right plan/maneuvre for White in such positions?} 16. Nd2 $1 {
The knight has nothing to do on f3, so we are rerouting it to c4 via d2.
Meanwhile, the e4-pawn also gets more secure as we can always protect it with
f2-f3, or possibly, in some cases, we can gain more space with f2-f4, g2-g4
etc.} *

