{[#] How to proceed with White?} 18. Bd1 $1 {The bishop on a4 is rather
annoying, so it's well worth trading it.} Bxd1 19. Rfxd1 $14 {White has a very
comfortable one-sided type of position where he can either try to put pressure
on the queenside by means of the typical a2-a4-a5, or gain more space on the
kingside with g2-g3, Kg2, h2-h4 etc.} *

