{[#] What is Black's only equalizing idea?} 14... a6 $1 15. a4 b5 $1 {Black's
only chance to make use of his better development is to open up the position
quickly, or else White's static advantage will ensure him of a better game.}
16. axb5 axb5 17. Bxb5 exd5 18. Bc6 Ra6 19. Bxd5 Rd6 $1 {And ...Bf5 is about
to regain the pawn with equality, please see the chapter on 9.Rb1 with 10...
